{"tid":1214832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實坐地鐵，對一班唔敢出街既人黎講真係一個好選擇","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:57:36.000Z","uid":72063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96c9d1989260f0b4515dd56209cb76a50fa3a838","tid":1214832,"uid":72063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"其實有好多人都係唔敢出街，上有高堂下有妻兒既人。<br />\n<br />\n咁坐地鐵真係適合呢班人去做，好過留係屋企睇live再係ig Facebook 出個支持post。<br />\n<br />\n因為坐地鐵既快捷又方便，好似一條輸血管咁，全港咩地方都去到，咁方便點可以唔坐？<br />\n<br />\n重點係地鐵有個好處就係唔會塞車，除左上次打風搞到幾乎全香港人番唔到工咁濟，諗番起果次都幾混亂，好彩有地鐵咋，如果唔係日日都係咁都幾麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n重點係坐地鐵好合法，唔會無啦啦比人拉，又有冷氣，又安全，又舒適，一家大細都岩坐。<br />\n<br />\n你地話坐地鐵有幾多好處，所以我不嬲都支持地鐵"},{"pid":"8e56fbce5044b64a550c93a8085ea4df7676242f","tid":1214832,"uid":72063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf57c5eb611fedd286a1955ced459a4b1bb3458","tid":1214832,"uid":72063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72eb18a866301500f3e0964fb045868018405e3e","tid":1214832,"uid":72063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96cda8f080719f10ec338af536c0f1216cbcd6b","tid":1214832,"uid":72063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}